show.description:
A wealthy businessman unknowingly marries his long-lost childhood love, an amnesiac woman targeted by deceitful rivals, and must uncover the truth before it's too late.
Set against a backdrop of betrayal, mistaken identity, and forbidden love, Billionaire's Memory Loss Wife is a gripping tale of destiny and revenge.
